<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<link rel="icon" href="/assets/logo.png">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/styles/main.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/styles/home_signin.css">
	<title>Whisker Cove</title>
</head>
<body onload="localTime()">
	<div id="page">
		<!-- header -->
		<%- include('common/header.ejs') %>
		
		<!-- side menu -->
		<%- include('common/navbar.ejs') %>
		
		<!-- main content -->
		<main>
			<div class="section">
				<article class="first">
					<div class="text">
						<h4>Discover the Delightful World of Feline Charm</h4> <br>
						<p>
							Welcome to our adorable world of pets!
							Meet this lovely kitten, full of mischief and charm. <br><br>
							
							Whether they're chasing a ball of yarn or snuggling up for a nap, kittens always bring joy to our lives.
							At our sanctuary, we celebrate the unique personalities and playful antics of feline friends like this one. <br><br>
							
							Join us as we explore the wonderful world of cats, where every whisker twitch and purr is a moment of pure delight.
							Stay tuned for more heartwarming stories and delightful adventures with our furry companions!
						</p>
					</div>
					<img src="/assets/kitty.jpg" alt="Kitten">
				</article>
				<article class="second">
					<img src="/assets/puppy.jpg" alt="Puppy">
					<div class="text">
						<h4>Discover the Love Between Pets!</h4> <br>
						<p>
							At our pet website, we celebrate the special bond between different furry companions.
							It's a reminder that love knows no bounds, even among our beloved pets.
							Join us in celebrating the joy and companionship that pets bring into our lives! <br><br>
							
							Explore our resources on pet care, training tips, and heartwarming stories that highlight the beauty of the human-animal bond.
							Whether you're a dog person, a cat person, or love all animals, there's something here for everyone who cherishes the presence of a furry friend.
						</p>
					</div>
				</article>
			</div>
		</main>
		
		<!-- footer -->
		<%- include('common/footer.ejs') %>
	</div>
	<script src="/scripts/index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>